description: Returns the details for the Security Hub member accounts for the specified account IDs. An administrator account can be either the delegated Security Hub administrator account for an organization or an administrator account that enabled Security Hub manually. The results include both member accounts that are managed using Organizations and accounts that were invited manually.

nested_items.name: Members
nested_items.description: The list of details about the Security Hub member accounts.

nested_items.name: AccountId
nested_items.description: The Amazon Web Services account ID of the member account.

nested_items.name: Email
nested_items.description: The email address of the member account.

nested_items.name: AdministratorId
nested_items.description: The Amazon Web Services account ID of the Security Hub administrator account associated with this member account.

nested_items.name: MemberStatus
nested_items.description: The status of the relationship between the member account and its administrator account.
Created - Indicates that the administrator account added the member account, but has not yet invited the member account.
Invited - Indicates that the administrator account invited the member account. The member account has not yet responded to the invitation.
Enabled - Indicates that the member account is currently active. For manually invited member accounts, indicates that the member account accepted the invitation.
Removed - Indicates that the administrator account disassociated the member account.
Resigned - Indicates that the member account disassociated themselves from the administrator account.
Deleted - Indicates that the administrator account deleted the member account.

AccountSuspended - Indicates that an organization account was suspended from Amazon Web Services at the same time that the administrator account tried to enable the organization account as a member account.

nested_items.name: InvitedAt
nested_items.description: A timestamp for the date and time when the invitation was sent to the member account.

nested_items.name: UpdatedAt
nested_items.description: The timestamp for the date and time when the member account was updated.

nested_items.name: UnprocessedAccounts
nested_items.description: The list of Amazon Web Services accounts that could not be processed. For each account, the list includes the account ID and the email address.

nested_items.name: AccountId
nested_items.description: An Amazon Web Services account ID of the account that was not processed.

nested_items.name: ProcessingResult
nested_items.description: The reason that the account was not processed.
